1. DESCRIPTION

Personal configuration of the Linux kernel with patch Con Kolivas.
Initrd not needed.

2. HARDWARE DESCRIPTION

Motherboard:	ASUS M2N-E
CPU:		AMD Athlon 64 3500+
RAM:		Kingston 2GB
Graphic card:	XFX nVidia GTS 250 512MB
Hard Disk:	1x Seagate 80GB 7200rpm 8MB
		2x Seagate 320GB 7200rpm 16MB (Mirrored)
Optical drive:	1x Plextor PX-810SA
		1x Plextor PX-716A
Network:	Integrated Ethernet 10/100/1000
		External wireless USB stick (rt-73)

2. HOW TO COMPILE

$ Copy the .config in the kernel source directory (Con Kolivas patched).
$ make modules_prepare
$ make all
$ make headers_install
# make install
# update-grub
$ make clean && make mrproper
